title: "Owner" means a person who receives rent for the use of the land or building or would be entitled to
clause_text: "Owner" means a person who receives rent for the use of the land or building or would be entitled to do so if it were let, and includes: an authorised agent or trustee who receives such rent on behalf of the owner;
